---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Hero from "../../components/Hero.astro";
import TrackListSection from "../../components/TrackListSection.astro";
import FullAlbumSection from "../../components/FullAlbumSection.astro";
import SideSheet from "../../components/SideSheet.astro";
import { upcomingItems } from "../../data/upcoming";
---

<Layout title="Chapter 1">

<div class="chapter-bg" style="--bg-image: url('/images/template.png');">
<div class="chapter-content container">
  <SideSheet title="Upcoming" items={upcomingItems} />
  <Hero eyebrow="Chapter 1"
        title="Resonance of Rust"
        backHref="/"/>

<section class="section section-narrative">
<div class="narrative">
  <p>
    Every road leaves something behind.
  </p>

  <p>
    “Resonance of Rust” is the first chapter in the quiet journey of Rusty Notebooks —<br />
    a collection of songs shaped by slow evenings,<br />
    old highways,<br />
    cedarwood smoke,<br />
    and the strange feeling of arriving somewhere<br />
    you might have been before.
  </p>

  <p>
    Some say this is where the story begins.<br />
    Others might say it’s where it finally ends.
  </p>

  <p>
    Between fading radio signals,<br />
    rain on old metal roofs,<br />
    and the warmth of a fire after a long road,<br />
    these songs trace the quiet spaces<br />
    between who we were…<br />
    and who we might become.
  </p>

  <p class="narrative-final">
    So take a seat by the fire,<br />
    let the road disappear behind you,<br />
    and follow the first chapter<br />
    of the Rusty Notebooks.
  </p>
</div>
</section>

